  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个导入任务的状态流转图。整体流程是从初始状态进入待处理，然后开始处理，最后要么成功导入，要么失败。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "PENDING",
        "PROCESSING",
        "IMPORTED",
        "FAILED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那失败之后有重试机制吗？还是直接结束？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FAILED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有重试的，FAILED可以回到PROCESSING重新执行。另外IMPORTED成功之后就直接结束了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FAILED",
        "PROCESSING",
        "IMPORTED",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程：起点到PENDING，PENDING到PROCESSING，然后PROCESSING分叉到IMPORTED和FAILED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "PENDING",
        "PROCESSING",
        "IMPORTED",
        "FAILED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，PENDING到PROCESSING的触发条件是\"Start Import\"，PROCESSING到IMPORTED是\"Import Successful\"，到FAILED是\"Import Failed\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PENDING",
        "PROCESSING",
        "IMPORTED",
        "FAILED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了所有迁移标签。现在补上重试路径：FAILED回到PROCESSING，标签是\"Retry Import\"，还有IMPORTED到终点的结束线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FAILED",
        "PROCESSING",
        "IMPORTED",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，重试那条线的标签应该是\"Retry Import\"，不是\"Retry\"，要和业务术语保持一致。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FAILED",
